article.description: — Jalen Myers scored 21 points as UT Martin beat Ecclesia 110-52 on Sunday.
article.headline: UT Martin wins 110-52 against Ecclesia
article.story: MARTIN, Tenn. -- — Jalen Myers scored 21 points as UT Martin beat Ecclesia 110-52 on Sunday. Myers also contributed six rebounds and five assists for the Skyhawks (6-4). Sebastian Mendoza added 18 points while going 6 of 8 from the floor, including 3 for 4 from 3-point range, and 3 for 4 from the line, and he also had 11 rebounds. Jordan Sears had 17 points and shot 6 for 11 (3 for 5 from 3-point range) and 2 of 3 from the free throw line. Ryan Reed finished with 17 points for the Royals. Ecclesia also got eight points from Kengi Bryant. Jerry Boston also recorded eight points. NEXT UP UT Martin plays NC State on the road on Tuesday, and Ecclesia visits UAPB on Monday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
